#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Operations/ContentReadability/AudienceTargetedAdjustmentsOperation.php:25
#, fuzzy
msgid "Analyzes content readability and tone to ensure it matches the target audience`s expectations. Provides recommendations for adjustments to improve audience targeting."
