#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Operations/ContentQualityAndLength/ReadabilityValidationOperation.php:27
#, fuzzy
msgid "Analyzes content readability using Flesch-Kincaid scores, sentence complexity, paragraph structure, passive voice usage, and transition word frequency. Provides detailed metrics and suggestions for improving content readability."
