#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:968
#, fuzzy
msgid "Your website does not serve WebP images or provide fallbacks for browsers that support this format. Implementing WebP with proper fallbacks can significantly improve page load times while ensuring compatibility across all browsers."
